* 2004: with Ben Street / Kresten Osgood &amp; Bryan Carrott - &quot;Purple Violets&quot; (Stunt)
* 2004: with Ben Street / Kresten Osgood - &quot;Violet Violets&quot; (Stunt)
* 2007: with Dave Holland / Barry Altschul - &quot;&quot; (Pi, 2012)

